{"tid":746568,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本擬提早修改教科書 明年列釣魚台為「領土」","createTime":"2018-07-17T15:49:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T21:14:50.000Z","uid":79563,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"788944c63dc831d617ca65698b62a3d947acc146","tid":746568,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T15:49:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180717/large/1531831871_8653.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180717%2Flarge%2F1531831871_8653.jpg&h=f19d533e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本文部科學省今日宣佈高中教改過渡方案，提出明年的新學年起，提前修改地理歷史及公民科目的部份內容，將支那、台灣和日本均宣稱擁有主權的尖閣諸島，及日本與南韓有爭議的竹島，列為日本固有領土，不存在主權問題。此一舉措料將引起支那強烈反應。<br />\n<br />\n共同社報道，日本文部科學省為了確保順利導入從2022年度入學新生的高中學習指導要領，今天公佈將從2019年度起實施過渡措施方案。文科省今天起就過渡方案公開徵集意見。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，文科省今年3月曾公示的下一期指導要領中，「地理綜合」科目首次寫明竹島和尖閣諸島為「固有領土」，在「歷史綜合」科目寫入「提及竹島、尖閣諸島編入日本」。對於公民領域新設的「公共」科目，要領提出需涉及日本努力和平解決竹島問題以及尖閣諸島不存在主權問題。"},{"pid":"d2874127da70fceb0513e7fe4c06b9ebbfaf6baa","tid":746568,"uid":30085,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T15:50:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e83922dfd655d66c1555d01be5acc6dcf433dd2","tid":746568,"uid":51183,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T16:21:32.000Z","msg":"日本國政府自1972年5月15日沖繩返還後<br />\n一直有效行駛尖閣諸島主權"},{"pid":"7187f32997c77cca9fe180b9487df9bef921459b","tid":746568,"uid":45368,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T16:26:05.000Z","msg":"釣魚台係中華民國架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"158002526c03ff2507e6aa4c2139934d6ec0a334","tid":746568,"uid":97240,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T19:29:30.000Z","msg":"又可以見支那人吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bccf1deb3fe0712e7c035043412a2bb6ec23bd4d","tid":746568,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T19:40:18.000Z","msg":"打蛇隨棍上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個時勢上去起埋雷達站派人守都唔怕支狗做啲咩"},{"pid":"40a726255033818d302f049dd37a4bde14de54a0","tid":746568,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T20:30:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e7cbbb5dbeff52fa7a5cbbe0b7320ff07c84fa8","tid":746568,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T21:14:50.000Z","msg":"學南海咁將尖閣諸島起雷達站同機場跑道同碼頭"}]}